ib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/565"},"text":"64 Stat. 565","children":[],"tail":"), because of sections 5 and 8 of Reorganization Plan No. 1 of 1953 (5 App. U.S.C.) and 20:3441 and 3507. In clause (3), the reference to the Vocational Education Act of 1946 (ch. 541, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/49/1488"},"text":"49 Stat. 1488","children":[],"tail":") is omitted because that Act was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1968-10-16/s103"},"text":"section 103 of the Act of October 16, 1968","children":[],"tail":" ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/576"},"text":"Public Law 90–576","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/1091"},"text":"82 Stat. 1091","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id748706a4-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id748706a5-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2019—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/7/s6/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–7, § 6(1)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (a) generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The national officers of the corporation are a student president, four student vice presidents (one from each of four regions of the United States established in the bylaws for purposes of administration of the corporation), a student secretary, an executive secretary, a treasurer, and a national advisor.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/7/s6/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–7, § 6(4)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “, except that—” in introductory provisions and pars. (1) to (3) which related to the national advisor, executive secretary, and treasurer, respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/7/s6/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–7, § 6(2)","children":[],"tail":", (3), redesignated subsec. (c) as (b) and struck out former subsec. (b) which read as follows: “"},{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Board of Student Officers","children":[],"tail":".—The national student officers of the corporation comprise a board of student officers. The board of student officers shall advise and make recommendations to the board of directors about the activities and business of the corporation.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (c), (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/7/s6/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–7, § 6(3)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (d) as (c). Former subsec. (c) redesignated (b)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
